snippet.title: The Caribbean Sail - Route Planning
snippet.description:
The most splendiferously deadly game about sailing the ocean now lets you explore the world! 

Contract and die of dysentery in 9 new locations!

Get impaled by a narwhal in Iceland!

What are you waiting for? Your "fortune" awaits!

Full expansion log: https://steamcommunity.com/games/TCS/announcements/detail/1666776116214568189
